Lola Kirke https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lola_Kirke 0 Lola Clementine C Kirke (born 27 September 1990) is an English-born American actress and singer-songwriter, best known for her starring roles in Mistress America and the Amazon Studios television series Mozart in the Jungle. She is also known for her supporting role in David Fincher's Gone Girl.
